# Implementation Plan - Cart Checkout Tool

We will implement a new tool called `process_cart_checkout` in the `shopping-assistant` agent. This tool receives a cart ID, user ID, and an optional discount code to apply a discount, process the order, and produce a unique order confirmation.

## Proposed Changes

### Database & State Setup

